.section.new-home-content.casestudy-content
  p
    |Being an on-demand app for home services, a seamless mobile experience was at the heart of the product strategy. <br> One of the key branding goals was to position Housejoy as a professional and high quality service and not just another marketplace for home services. Hence, we decided to give it a little sophisticated look and feel.
